moduleInfo.moduleDesc: Unofficial module to read manga from natomanga.com

javascriptConfig.javaScript: try {          const savedData = document.getElementById('ketsu-final-data');          const parsedJson = JSON.parse(savedData.innerHTML);          const items = document.querySelectorAll('.slide .item');          const empty = [{ key: '', value: '' }];          const data = [];          items.forEach(item => {            const img = item.querySelector('img')?.src;            const titleEl = item.querySelector('.slide-caption h3 a');            const title = titleEl?.innerText?.trim();            const link = titleEl?.href;            if (title && img && link) {              data.push({                image: { url: img, method: 'get', headers: empty, httpBody: null },                title: title,                link: { url: link, method: 'get', headers: empty, httpBody: null },                description: '', field1: '', field2: '', field3: '', field4: '', isChapter: false              });            }          });          const output = [{            cellDesing: 'normal1',            orientation: 'vertical',            defaultLayout: 'wide',            paging: '',            section: { sectionName: 'Popular Manga', separator: true },            layout: null,            data: data          }];          savedData.innerHTML = JSON.stringify(output);        } catch(e) { console.log(e); }

try {          const savedData = document.getElementById('ketsu-final-data');          const parsedJson = JSON.parse(savedData.innerHTML);          const items = document.querySelectorAll('.panel-search-story .story_item');          const empty = [{ key: '', value: '' }];          const data = [];          items.forEach(item => {            const img = item.querySelector('img')?.src;            const titleEl = item.querySelector('.story_name a');            const title = titleEl?.innerText?.trim();            const link = titleEl?.href;            if (title && img && link) {              data.push({                image: { url: img, method: 'get', headers: empty, httpBody: null },                title: title,                link: { url: link, method: 'get', headers: empty, httpBody: null },                description: '', field1: '', field2: '', field3: '', field4: '', isChapter: false              });            }          });          const output = [{            cellDesing: 'normal1',            orientation: 'vertical',            defaultLayout: 'wide',            paging: '',            section: { sectionName: 'Search Results', separator: true },            layout: null,            data: data          }];          savedData.innerHTML = JSON.stringify(output);        } catch(e) { console.log(e); }
